![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b3d8b61c-7dc7-4339-8757-3bd88e5c1753/Screenshot+2024-06-17+170902.png?format=original)

RAW opens with the surprise return of Seth Rollins. Rollins says he’s back for one reason. He’s about to declare he wants in the MITB when Damien Priest inturrupts,

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f3a7ad6d-51b5-4953-b853-0a75e7b0a86e/448337297_1493924861505646_5248753487536750546_n.jpg?format=original)

Priest tells Rollins this is no longer Monday Night Rollins. Rollins says he and Priest are alike. They both won MITB, they both were in a faction. But Rollins grew a set. He asks what kind of Champion is Damien Priest?  
  
Priest is HEATED. He says Rollins doesn’t need MITB or anything. At Money in the Bank he will gladly give Seth Rollins a shot at the World Heavyweight Championship. Seth asks if this is a trap? Priest is straight up!!  
  
Rollins accepts!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bcf818fa-a862-464b-a35a-dc1c440b4cbb/448511992_1189226735449810_7785075908225547025_n.jpg?format=original)

Chad Gable tries to get himself a rematch for the IC Title. Adam Pierce says Gable will have to fight his way back up the ladder like anyone else. Gable blames his family, of course.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/585577ba-c185-4a72-93f4-9963b324e81e/448187188_1114374593191707_7192586506769879677_n.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_BRAUN STROWMAN DEF. CHAD GABLE_**
    

Gable blames the Academy... He took Maxxine's crutch from her and was forcing her to walk away from the ring on her bad ankle. Tonawanda gets involved. Gable shoves him down. OTIS HAS FINALLY HAD ENOUGH AND SNAPS ON GABLE. He pushes Gable off of his feet.

Gable is begging Otis to stop. Otis walks away with his friends.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/07b0e547-3597-4241-adbb-6c17a62bf3ed/received_480046681085676.jpeg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e215ec71-a2d2-48bf-8a2e-1dac8aef976a/received_841948031146708.jpeg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/85a654cd-b235-4114-b65b-dbfee0d6cf74/received_452676351042691.jpeg?format=original)

Damien Priest wants to know why Finn Balor took the hotel key. Balor doesn’t like Priest tone. Says he took the key to prevent Dom from using it.

Priest asks what is Balor gonna do if he wins the Money in the Bank briefcase. Balor says he’s going to keep it real… if he gets the briefcase, he’s going to cash it in…. on Cody Rhodes. He laughs and says Priest can trust him

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/702c48b3-d202-4e3c-9ee5-a444f2a0c2b3/received_1379234526079937.jpeg?format=original)

