*   ## **_MONEY IN THE BANK QUALIFYING MATCH: IYO SKY DEF. KIANA JAMES AND ZELINA VEGA_**
    

Liv Morgan made her way out to ringside to distract Zelina Vega. This allowed Iyo to hit the moonsauly on James for her spot in the MITB.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/10833ab6-397e-4054-8808-844675d0cb8c/received_447066474795492.jpeg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3dc25ca6-4cb9-4c85-a157-0e9063554e38/received_2274237012747058.jpeg?format=original)

Sami Zayn is going to cut a promo when he’s interrupted by Bron Breakker who wants the Intercontinental Championship.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6962507f-ab42-4c3f-9253-3f6ef22edd10/received_447896137967510.jpeg?format=original)

Sheamus interrupts them both to say he’ll do whatever it takes to get the one title he’s never had in WWE.

Bron tells Sheamus nobody cares about his sob stories or anything like that. Bron is going to kick Sheamus ass for standing in his way.

Sami Zayn says he’s going to Adam Pearce to set up Bron Breakker vs Sheamus tonight. Winner gets Sami Zayn

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e64ff01a-8fb0-429e-82f7-d72e91772946/received_2313354928874733.jpeg?format=original)

The spirit of Uncle Howdy continues to loom over the ring as we head into

*   ## **_CARLITO DEF. DRAGON LEE_**
    

Liv Morgan comes out in Dom's vest. Zelina attacks Liv. A brawl begins between LWO, Liv, Dom and JD. The distraction allows Carlito to take out Dragon Lee with the backbreaker and win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c3415166-5982-4a21-93fc-01b0877e53d1/20240617_184555.jpg?format=original)

Otis tells Chad Gable that he’s leaving him and that he’s done.

Chad Gable says that hes going to do what Otis never could and win the MITB Briefcase and successfully cash-in to become World Champion

* * *

