*   ## **_NUMBER ONE CONTENDERS MATCH: BRON BREAKKER VS SHEAMUS_** _ENDS IN NO CONTEST_
    

Beefy, meaty. Big time Heavyweight match between Bron and Sheamus that ends in DQ when Ludwig attacks Sheamus.

Ludwig runs around the ring to dropkick Sheamus leg into the stairs the way he did Giovanni Vinci. But he gets intercepted by Bron Breakker with a massive spear.

